# Spec traceability ([CFHA-VER-005])

If you edit a **SHALL** in `openspec/specs/*/spec.md`: keep the bracketed `[CFHA-REQ-…]` / `[CFHA-VER-…]` ID stable, update **`docs/spec-test-traceability.md`**, and add the ID to pytest docstrings or helm unittest comments for listed evidence files. Run **`./ci.sh`** (includes `scripts/check_spec_traceability.py`).
